# Virtual environments
**/.venv/
**/venv/
.env

# Python
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/

# Kortext auth — session cookies, treat as a credential. NEVER commit.
**/auth-state.json

# Scraped textbook content — likely copyrighted, personal use only. NEVER commit.
kortext/corpus/*
!kortext/corpus/.gitkeep

# Recon diagnostic output (may contain live tokens before redaction)
**/probe_out/
kortext/recon/network_log.txt

# Converted slide output (default local dir)
slides-output/

# Root CLAUDE.md — local CC context, not part of the public repo.
# Anchored leading slash so kortext/CLAUDE.md (tracked architecture ref) is unaffected.
/CLAUDE.md

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
